content.p: The Language Centre at University of Nottingham Malaysia (UNM) enjoys an international reputation for outstanding teaching. We offer French, German, Japanese, Korean, Spanish and Mandarin courses for students, corporate clients and partner institutions. The Language Centre will provide you with 20-40 hours in-semester immersive and practical courses and fantastic summer schools. Note: These courses are currently unavailable at the moment. telephone: +6 (03) 8924 8693 fax: +6 (03) 8924 8020
